{"word":"μισθοδοτέω","slug":"μισθοδοτέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μισθοδοτέω</b></el> <el>(μισθοδοτέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><p/><i>to pay wages</i>, <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>: —<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to furnish with pay</i>, Decret. <a href='S:apud (quoted in)'>ap.</a> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:μισθοδότης'><el>μισθοδότης</el></a>\n"}]}